Achievements.Name: Become Someone
Achievements.Description: Create any wrestler in Create A Wrestler mode.

Achievements.Name: Get in the Ring
Achievements.Description: Complete any stunt in Quick Play Mode on Average Joe Difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Just the Two of Us
Achievements.Description: Complete an entire Head To Head match on Average Joe Difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Champ of the Ring
Achievements.Description: Complete an entire Exhibition Mode match on Average Joe Difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Just the Two of Us, 2X
Achievements.Description: Complete an entire Head To Head match on Hardcore Difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Just the Beginning
Achievements.Description: Complete the Career Mode on Average Joe Difficulty.

Achievements.Name: I am Hardcore
Achievements.Description: Complete the Career Mode on Hardcore Difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Roger, Dodger
Achievements.Description: Complete the Entrance without getting hit by any object.

Achievements.Name: Profit, Prophet
Achievements.Description: Earn over 100,000 points in a single stunt.

Achievements.Name: Can't Touch This!
Achievements.Description: Complete the Irish Whip Stunt without getting hit by your opponent.

Achievements.Name: Blockbuster
Achievements.Description: Complete the Ladder Bash Stunt without getting hit by your opponent.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Punch
Achievements.Description: Finish your opponent off with a punch in Trade Blows.

Achievements.Name: Be Super, Man
Achievements.Description: Perform a high flying splash in Aerial Assault.

Achievements.Name: Chiropractor Disaster
Achievements.Description: Perform a piledriver in the Body Slam stunt.

Achievements.Name: Flippin' Perfect
Achievements.Description: Flip your opponent 3 times in the Grapple stunt without ever being flipped.

Achievements.Name: Pin and Win
Achievements.Description: Successfully pin your opponent for a 3 count in the Pin To Win stunt.

Achievements.Name: Failure to Fail
Achievements.Description: Fight your way out of the corner and knock your opponent out of the ring in the On The Ropes stunt.

Achievements.Name: Getting a Sandwich, BRB
Achievements.Description: Player leaves sensor area in middle of any stunt.

Achievements.Name: Bad Altitude
Achievements.Description: Successfully throw your opponent out of the ring via a Choke Slam.

Achievements.Name: Hulkstering Up
Achievements.Description: Win a match in Trade Blows via Hulkstering Up.

Achievements.Name: If the Boot Fits
Achievements.Description: Successfully perform a Hulk Hogan "Boot" attack in The Irish Whip stunt.

Achievements.Name: Listen Like the Great One
Achievements.Description: Perform the Hulk Hogan Listen pose to the crowd in the Entrance stunt.

Achievements.Name: Armed and Dangerous
Achievements.Description: Grab a chair in air, in the Chair Hit stunt.
